Adolph Coors Co, e say William K. Coors, di chairman, e assume di oda responsibilities of Presido, e succeed Jeffrey H. Coors.

Jephthrey Coors wey be 44 years don dey president since 1985 when e follow im papa Jose do di work.

But di Breeze talk sey Jeffrey Coors use im mind drop di position make e focus on top di power wey im get for Coors technology co, small unit of coors wey e don dey run for many years.

One coors tok sey di company no believe sey di move go add more power to William Coors, or reduce di influence of Jeffrey Coors, Peter Coors, or Joseph Coors Jr wey be di three operating unit.

E no suppose be demotion now, di spokesman yarn sey na pete, and Jeff and Joe Jr de don take over di reins, and dem dey do most of di work.

We no tink sey dis one go affect o.

Jephthrey, Peter and Josef Jr. na brodas.

William Coors na im uncle.

Jephthrey, Peter, Joseph Jr., William, and Joseph Sr. Dis na di company board.

Peter Coors dey kontrol Coors Brewing Co, di fourth largest brewery wey dem produce for one million, 24 billion adolph Coors $1.52 billion for 1988 sales.

Joseph Jr. dey sell Coors Ceramics Co, di oda operating unit wey get about $150 million for 1988 sales.

